      "actionDesc": "Introduced in House",
      "text": "<p><strong>Veterans Employment Readiness Yield Act of 2025 or the VERY Act of 2025&nbsp;</strong></p><p>This bill revises terminology used under the Veteran Readiness and Employment program, specifically by replacing the use of <em>employment handicap</em> with <em>employment barrier</em>.</p>",
